---
description: Use migration.sh for DB tasks instead of raw ORM commands
globs:
alwaysApply: false
---

- Always use `./scripts/migration.sh` for database operations
- Use:
  - `./scripts/migration.sh generate` to generate migrations
  - `./scripts/migration.sh migrate` to run migrations
  - `./scripts/migration.sh seed` to seed data
- If Using Docker
  - `./scripts/migration.sh generate-container` to generate migrations
  - `./scripts/migration.sh migrate-container` to run migrations
  - `./scripts/migration.sh seed-container` to seed data
- Do not call raw Prisma/TypeORM/Bun migration commands directly
